'''高铁酸盐'''中的高铁酸根是一种[[无机化学|无机]][[阴离子|阴离子]]，[[化学式|化学式]][FeO<sub>4</sub>]<sup>2-</sup>。它[[光敏性#在化学中|对光敏感]]，使得化合物和溶解有它的溶液呈淡紫色。其为已知最强的对水稳定的氧化物质之一。尽管它被归为[[盐基|弱碱]]，高铁酸盐浓溶液仍具有腐蚀性，且会烧伤皮肤，只能在高pH环境中稳定存在。

== 命名法 ==

''ferrate''通常指代高铁酸根，尽管它可以指其它含铁[[阴离子|阴离子]]，其中有许多比[FeO<sub>4</sub>]<sup>2-</sup>的盐更为常见。这包括有强烈还原性的[[四羰基铁酸二钠|四羰基铁酸二钠]]Na<sub>2</sub>[Fe(CO)<sub>4</sub>]和三价铁络合物四氯合铁酸根[FeCl<sub>4</sub>]<sup>-</sup>。铁的[[含氧阴离子|含氧阴离子]]铁(V)酸根[FeO<sub>4</sub>]<sup>3-</sup>和铁(IV)酸根[FeO<sub>4</sub>]<sup>4-</sup>也同样存在，但对它们的研究较少。这些也称为高铁酸根。<ref name="hill">{{cite book
| title = Chemistry in context
| author1 = Graham Hill
| author2 = John Holman
| edition = 5th
| publisher = Nelson Thornes
| year = 2000
| isbn = 0-17-448276-0
| page = 202
}}</ref>

== 合成 ==

高铁酸盐可在[[碱|碱性条件]]用强氧化剂在[[水溶液|水溶液]]中[[氧化还原反应|氧化]]铁，或加热固态的铁屑和粉状硝酸钾的混合物而形成。<ref name="sharma">{{cite book
| title = Text Book Of Coordination Chemistry
| author = R. K. Sharma
| publisher = Discovery Publishing House
| year = 2007
| isbn = 81-8356-223-X
| pages = 124–125
}}</ref>

例如，在碱性[[溶液|溶液]]中加热[[氢氧化铁|氢氧化铁]]与[[次氯酸钠|次氯酸钠]]制备高铁酸盐：<ref name="wulfsberg"/>

:2 {{chem|Fe(OH)|3}} + 3 {{chem|OCl|-}} + 4 {{chem|OH|-}} → 2 {{chem|[FeO|4|]|2-}} + 5 {{chem|H|2|O}} + 3 {{chem|Cl|-}}

通常让阴离子以[[钡|钡]]盐的形式沉淀出来，形成[[高铁酸钡|高铁酸钡]]。<ref name="wulfsberg"/> 

== 性质 ==

高铁酸根阴离子不稳定，在中性<ref name="sharma"/>或酸性[[pH|pH]]环境中会分解为三价铁：<ref name="wulfsberg">{{cite book
| title = Principles of descriptive inorganic chemistry
| url = https://archive.org/details/principlesofdesc0000wulf_i2q0
| author = Gary Wulfsberg
| publisher = University Science Books
| year = 1991
| isbn = 0-935702-66-0
| pages = [https://archive.org/details/principlesofdesc0000wulf_i2q0/page/142 142]–143
}}</ref>

:{{chem|[FeO|4|]|2-}} + 3 {{chem|e|-}} + 8 {{chem|H|+}} {{eqm}} {{chem|Fe|3+}} + 4 {{chem|H|2|O}}

还原过程中间体中铁的氧化态有+5和+4<ref name="wiberg"/>。这些阴离子甚至比高铁酸根更活泼<ref name="bergeron"/>。碱性条件下高铁酸根更稳定，pH为8或9时能存在约8至9小时<ref name="bergeron">{{cite book
| title = The Development of Iron Chelators for Clinical Use
| url = https://archive.org/details/developmentofiro0000unse
| editor = Raymond J. Bergeron
| author = Gary M. Brittenham
| publisher = CRC Press
| year = 1994
| isbn = 0-8493-8679-9
| pages = [https://archive.org/details/developmentofiro0000unse/page/37 37]–38
}}</ref>。

高铁酸盐的水溶液较稀时为粉红色，较浓时为深红或紫色<ref name="wiberg">{{cite book
| title = Inorganic chemistry
| author1 = Egon Wiberg
| author2 = Nils Wiberg
| author3 = Arnold Frederick Holleman
| publisher = Academic Press
| year = 2001
| isbn = 0-12-352651-5
| pages = 1457–1458
}}</ref><ref>{{cite book
| title = Oxford dictionary of chemistry
| editor = John Daintith
| edition = 5th
| publisher = Oxford University Press
| year = 2004
| isbn = 0-19-860918-3
| page = 235
}}</ref>。与[[高锰酸盐|高锰酸盐]]相比，高铁酸盐是更强的[[氧化剂|氧化剂]]<ref name="mackay">{{cite book
| title = Introduction to modern inorganic chemistry
| author1 = Kenneth Malcolm Mackay
| author2 = Rosemary Ann Mackay
| author3 = W. Henderson
| edition = 6th
| publisher = CRC Press
| year = 2002
| isbn = 0-7487-6420-8
| pages = 334–335
}}</ref>，可以将[[铬|三价铬]]氧化成[[重铬酸盐|重铬酸盐]]<ref>{{cite book
| title = Text Book Of Inorganic Chemistry
| author = Amit Arora
| publisher = Discovery Publishing House
| year = 2005
| isbn = 81-8356-013-X
| pages = 691–692
}}</ref>，或将[[氨|氨]]氧化成[[氮|氮]]分子<ref>{{cite web | url = https://kb.osu.edu/dspace/bitstream/1811/36335/1/OH_WRC_444.pdf | title = Oxidation of Ammonia in Water by Ferrates(VI) and (IV) | author = Karlis Svanks | date = June 1976 | format = PDF | page = 3 | publisher = Water Resources Center, Ohio State University | accessdate = 2010-05-04 }}</ref>。

高铁酸盐是优秀的[[消毒剂|消毒剂]]，能移除并杀死[[病毒|病毒]]。<ref>{{cite book
| title = Environmental chemistry
| url = https://archive.org/details/environmentalche0000mana_08ed
| author = Stanley E. Manahan
| edition = 8th
| publisher = CRC Press
| year = 2005
| isbn = 1-56670-633-5
| page = [https://archive.org/details/environmentalche0000mana_08ed/page/234 234]
}}</ref>

高铁酸根离子有两个[[不成对电子|不成对电子]]，因此具有[[顺磁性|顺磁性]]。其为[[四面体形分子构型|四面体形分子构型]]。<ref name="wiberg"/>

